                                tr
                                    td.showTo-md: img(src="unit_1/module_2/assets/images/act_14-a.jpg", alt="" class="u-responsive-img w100")
                                    td.ta-c Future Continuous
                                    td: div(class="row") 
                                        div(class="col-flex ta-c") At 8:00 PM tonight, John 
                                            strong (1. wash) 
                                            span(class="c-textField"): input(type="text" placeholder="Text here..." class="c-input js-escribir")
                                            br
                                            | the dishes.
                                    td: div(class="row") 
                                        div(class="col-flex ta-c") At 8:00 PM tonight, the dishes
                                            strong (2. Wash) 
                                            span(class="c-textField"): input(type="text" placeholder="Text here..." class="c-input js-escribir")
                                            br
                                            | by John.
                                tr
                                    td.showTo-md: img(src="unit_1/module_2/assets/images/act_14-b.jpg", alt="" class="u-responsive-img w100")
                                    td.ta-c Future Perfect
                                    td: div(class="row") 
                                        div(class="col-flex ta-c") They 
                                            strong (3. complete) #[span(class="c-textField"): input(type="text" placeholder="Text here..." class="c-input js-escribir")]
                                            br
                                            | the assignment before the class ends.
                                    td: div(class="row") 
                                        div(class="col-flex ta-c") The assignment
                                            strong (4. complete)
                                            span(class="c-textField"): input(type="text" placeholder="Text here..." class="c-input js-escribir")
                                            br
                                            | before the class ends.
                                tr
                                    td.showTo-md: img(src="unit_1/module_2/assets/images/act_14-c.jpg", alt="" class="u-responsive-img w100")
                                    td.ta-c Future Perfect Continuous
                                    td: div(class="row")
                                        div(class="col-flex ta-c") The famous artist
                                            strong (5. paint) #[span(class="c-textField"): input(type="text" placeholder="Text here..." class="c-input js-escribir")]
                                            br
                                            | the mural for over six months by the time it is finished.
